  "subject": "VF Module to stay at Index 0 (first position) - Not Moveable.",
  "commit_message": "VF Module to stay at Index 0 (first position) - Not Moveable.\n\nIssue-ID: VID-861\n\nCurrently, the base VFModule, like other modules is also draggable. We would like the VFModule to retain the position at index 0 (first position) and not moveable when the user tries. This user story makes sure this behavior is enforced.\n\nSigned-off-by: ikram <ikram@research.att.com>\nChange-Id: I0082f82f644725280f9f325515ae3784a5868a2f\n",
